OL,3,CCan Trump actually withdraw from Nato?
OL,5,FBy ITV News Producer Hannah Ward-
OL,6,FGlenton
OL,8,FUS President Donald Trump has said
OL,9,Fmultiple times that he is considering
OL,10,Fleaving Nato after allies have not
OL,11,Fbeen forthcoming in joining and
OL,12,Fsupporting his war with Iran.
OL,14,FAsked by The Telegraph on Wednesday
OL,15,Fwhether he would reconsider the US'
OL,16,Fmembership, Trump said: "I was never
OL,17,Fswayed by Nato. I always knew they
OL,18,Fwere a paper tiger, and Putin knows
OL,19,Fthat too, by the way."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
