OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1775135469
OL,3,CCan Trump actually withdraw from Nato?
OL,5,FBut can the president really remove
OL,6,Fthe US from Nato? ITV News explains.
OL,8,FHow does a country leave Nato?
OL,10,FNato came about when 12 countries from
OL,11,FEurope and North America signed the
OL,12,FNorth Atlantic Treaty in 1949,
OL,13,Fpledging to assist each other should
OL,14,Fthey come under attack.
OL,16,FArticle 13 of the treaty lays out the
OL,17,Fwithdrawal procedure:
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1775135469
OL,3,CCan Trump actually withdraw from Nato?
OL,5,F"After the Treaty has been in force
OL,6,Ffor 20 years, any Party may cease to
OL,7,Fbe a Party one year after its notice
OL,8,Fof denunciation has been given to the
OL,9,FGovernment of the United States of
OL,10,FAmerica, which will inform the
OL,11,FGovernments of the other Parties of
OL,12,Fthe deposit of each notice of
OL,13,Fdenunciation."
OL,15,FSince 1969, any country has been free
OL,16,Fto leave Nato - but none have ever
OL,17,Fchosen to do so.
OL,19,FCan Trump make that decision by
OL,20,Fhimself?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
