PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1775135469
OL,3,CCan Trump actually withdraw from Nato?
OL,5,FUS Congress passed a law in 2023 that
OL,6,Fmeans the country could only withdraw
OL,7,Ffrom Nato with the advice and consent
OL,8,Fof the 100-member Senate - with two-
OL,9,Fthirds of senators in agreement - or
OL,10,Fan act of Congress.
OL,12,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,13,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,14,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,15,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,17,FThe bill was enacted while Joe Biden
OL,18,Fwas president, but it was co-sponsored
OL,19,Fby Democratic Senator Tim Kaine and
OL,20,Fthen-Senator Marco Rubio, who is now
OL,21,Fthe US secretary of state.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
