OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1775135469
OL,3,CCan Trump actually withdraw from Nato?
OL,5,FIf Trump did pull the US out of Nato,
OL,6,Fthere could be legal repercussions
OL,7,Fgiven it is explicitly banned in US
OL,8,Flaw.
OL,10,FBut could Trump make it happen anyway?
OL,12,FThe US president has become more and
OL,13,Fmore vocal about wanting to leave Nato
OL,14,Fand under international law, a
OL,15,Fnation's head of state technically
OL,16,Fdoes have the power to withdraw from a
OL,17,Ftreaty if it allows - as Nato does -
OL,18,Fand if the country adheres to the
OL,19,Fconditions laid out in the treaty.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
