PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1775135469
OL,3,CCan Trump actually withdraw from Nato?
OL,5,FEven if the US doesn't leave Nato, it
OL,6,Fcould cause a lot of disruption to
OL,7,Fother member states.
OL,9,FTrump's rhetoric around the alliance
OL,10,Fhas already discredited its power, and
OL,11,Fhas contributed to "the worst crisis
OL,12,FNato has ever confronted", according
OL,13,Fto former US representative to Nato
OL,14,FIvo Daalder.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
