CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1775135469
OL,3,CCan Trump actually withdraw from Nato?
OL,5,F"Military alliances are at their core,
OL,6,Fbased on trust: the confidence that if
OL,7,FI am attacked, you will come help
OL,8,Fdefend. That trust has been stretched
OL,9,Ffor years under Donald Trump's
OL,10,Fleadership. Has it finally been ripped
OL,11,Fapart and broken?" he wrote in a post
OL,12,Fon March 31.
OL,14,F"It's hard to see how any European
OL,15,Fcountry will now be able and willing
OL,16,Fto trust the United States to come to
OL,17,Fits defense. Hope, perhaps. But they
OL,18,Fcan't count on it," he added.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/11
